"= Display ON.<br>MAIN-: ACC MAIN on = Display OFF<br>OP-: OP enabled = "
"Display OFF."
msgstr ""
"標準：原廠行為。<br>MAIN+：ACC MAIN 開啟 = 螢幕開啟。<br>OP+：OP 啟用 = 螢幕"
"開啟。<br>MAIN-：ACC MAIN 開啟 = 螢幕關閉。<br>OP-：OP 啟用 = 螢幕關閉。"

